{"tid":720282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】彭博：加拿大擬就入口鋼材設置關稅及限額　防止中國大舉入口鋼鐵","createTime":"2018-06-27T20:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T04:33:40.000Z","uid":147314,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8fafff95024df8fcece3d24a44991dc42064d8bc","tid":720282,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:28:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/253036/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F253036%2F&d=zdDe3nbvRti%2BARZI9lqwTE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3cdbfd45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/253036/</a><br />\n<br />\n【貿易戰】彭博：加國擬為鋼材設限額阻中國傾銷　羅斯曾斥華迂迴入口美國避關稅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/27200941/image1530101240028.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F27200941%2Fimage1530101240028.png&h=4bc1b602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由美國總統特朗普掀起的貿易戰，已蔓延至其他國家。彭博通訊社引述消息指，加拿大擬就入口鋼材設置關稅及限額，有關措施更表明，是為防止中國等其他國家，向加國大舉入口鋼鐵。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述消息指，加國政府擬就入口鋼材設置關稅和入口限額，主要是針對中國等國家，向加拿大傾銷鋼材。消息指當局尚未有最終定案，但<span style=\"color: red;\">最快可於下周就公布</span>。"},{"pid":"59b6a85d5a7309b79db4f6ab7c1c9e127da870da","tid":720282,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:29:18.000Z","msg":"美國早前宣布向加拿大、歐盟和日本等鋼鐵徵收關稅，商務部長羅斯上周三（20日）出席參議院聽證會時，解釋這些措施是為了遏止中國向美國傾銷鋼材。他指表面上，中國過去5年向美國出口的鋼材數量下跌了，但其實只是把鋼材運到其他國家，再循這些國家把鋼材賣到美國，以避逃關稅和掩飾傾銷的行為。羅斯當時續稱，自美國向其他國家徵收關稅後，他們也採取措施配合，制止中國向境外傾銷鋼鐵，如歐盟在3月宣布對進口鋼鐵產品發起保障措施調查，日本亦決定部分中國製鋼鐵徵收反傾銷關稅。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報及白宮網頁）"},{"pid":"6d028b2e81090c9125047ea80e3eff5f0015eeec","tid":720282,"uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/21171110/image1529572228321.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F21171110%2Fimage1529572228321.png&h=fb27c2d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e6482e03e2c67238fc7c8137da402a057eee05e","tid":720282,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"唔係一早講咗，定香港唔得閒翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad90b06e6daf1fef843c1251a748cba2b8f047c6","tid":720282,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c567b0a98b960cee2120343ef7c019340a990ec2","tid":720282,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e6482e03e2c67238fc7c8137da402a057eee05e","tid":720282,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:31:51.000Z","msg":"唔係一早講咗，定香港唔得閒翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T20:59:56.000Z","msg":"遲咗少少，篇野幾個鐘前出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f600f48ab00379f036fd0cab6d8ad06daa10c6e","tid":720282,"uid":29874,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T21:19:54.000Z","msg":"當美國唔再接貨時，中國會諗盡一切辦法傾銷去其他國家，所以美國呢招真係逼其他國家一齊圍剿中國，你唔做，你就會變成下一個受害者"},{"pid":"ea2277f65051b3ed5e690e312d96dc743e604239","tid":720282,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T22:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add6d6589fa9237b3b22b250dbd5eaf9bea4c102","tid":720282,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T22:21:43.000Z","msg":"香港咁多偷工減料工程，拆曬重建就可以消化多餘產量"},{"pid":"07f5098a394c017061a4409cd71a43c9394f32b6","tid":720282,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit